# 1. BUSINESS REQUIREMENTS DOCUMENT (BRD)
## Project: Hotel Booking Insights and Cancellation Analysis
## 1.1 Project Overview
This system analyzes hotel booking data to understand trends, seasonality, customer preferences, and cancellation patterns. Insights help hotels reduce cancellations and improve occupancy rates.
## 1.2 Business Objectives
•	Identify peak booking seasons and customer patterns.
•	Reduce cancellations by understanding root causes.
•	Improve hotel occupancy rate.
•	Support management with data-driven strategy planning.
## 1.3 Problem Statement
Hotels experience high cancellation rates and seasonal fluctuations but lack clear insights into customer behavior and operational gaps.
## 1.4 Stakeholders
•	Hotel Manager
•	Reservation Team
•	Revenue Management Team
•	Marketing Department
•	Data Analytics Team
## 1.5 Scope
## In-Scope:
•	Booking trend analysis
•	Cancellation pattern analysis
•	Customer type analysis
•	Power BI visualization
## Out-of-Scope:
•	Hotel website booking system changes
•	Customer feedback collection
## 1.6 Business Requirements
•	R1: Analyze customer segments and booking patterns.
•	R2: Determine cancellation trends and possible causes.
•	R3: Power BI dashboard must show seasonal patterns.
•	R4: Provide recommendations to reduce cancellations.
## 1.7 Assumptions & Constraints
•	Data must include booking status and customer type.
•	No real-time updates required.
